dct_title_s: Electric power industry of Russia and nearby countries / Cartographic Information Center, INCOTEC
dct_description_sm: Map shows power plants, hydroelectric plants, electric transmission lines, characteristics of nuclear plants, and distribution of generating companies. Includes bar graphs, pie charts, a table, and a flow chart.
dct_spatial_sm: Russia. Russian Empire. Soviet Union. Former Soviet Republics
